PN,39301
SC,0001
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F393A1782397117
OL,3,CDarlington nurses due #187,000 in
OL,4,Cdamages over single-sex changing rooms
OL,5,Crow
OL,7,FNHS nurses in Darlington who took
OL,8,Ftheir employers to an employment
OL,9,Ftribunal over access to single-sex
OL,10,Fspaces in the workplace will receive
OL,11,F#187,000 in damages.
OL,13,FSeven nurses working at Darlington
OL,14,FMemorial Hospital brought the case
OL,15,Fagainst County Durham and Darlington
OL,16,FNHS Foundation Trust.
OL,1,W~k4~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}        G1/15
OL,2,W/*%+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNE Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,394,390,120,260,000,100
PN,39302
SC,0002
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F393A1782397117
OL,3,CDarlington nurses due #187,000 in
OL,4,Cdamages over single-sex changing rooms
OL,5,Crow
OL,7,FAn employment tribunal held in
OL,8,FNewcastle in January 2026 found that
OL,9,Fthe trust subjected the nurses to
OL,10,Fharassment by allowing a trans
OL,11,Fcolleague - a member of staff born
OL,12,Fmale who identified as a woman - to
OL,13,Fuse a female changing room without
OL,14,Fproviding a suitable alternative.
OL,16,FThe judgement found the nurses
OL,17,Fsuffered harassment which violated
OL,18,Ftheir dignity and created "a hostile,
OL,19,Fintimidating, humiliating and
OL,20,Fdegrading environment for them".
OL,1,W~k4~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}        G2/15
OL,2,W/*%+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNE Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,394,390,120,260,000,100
PN,39303
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F393A1782397117
OL,3,CDarlington nurses due #187,000 in
OL,4,Cdamages over single-sex changing rooms
OL,5,Crow
OL,7,FThe ruling said the trust also
OL,8,Fsubjected the nurses to harassment by
OL,9,Fnot taking their concerns seriously.
OL,11,FThe trust will now pay out #187,000 in
OL,12,Fdamages, separate to legal costs which
OL,13,Fwill be determined at a later date.
OL,15,FAn apology was issued by the trust
OL,16,Ffollowing the tribunal's decision, but
OL,17,Fthe trust has now apologised formally
OL,18,Fto each of the nurses in a letter in
OL,19,Fwhich it committed to a review of its
OL,20,Fpolicies in light of the decision.
OL,1,W~k4~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}        G3/15
OL,2,W/*%+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNE Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,394,390,120,260,000,100
PN,39304
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F393A1782397117
OL,3,CDarlington nurses due #187,000 in
OL,4,Cdamages over single-sex changing rooms
OL,5,Crow
OL,7,FThe letter reads: "We recognise that
OL,8,Fwe have a responsibility to provide a
OL,9,Fsafe, respectful and inclusive working
OL,10,Fenvironment for everyone and the
OL,11,FTribunal's findings make clear that we
OL,12,Fdid not get this right for you, for
OL,13,Fwhich the Trust expresses its sincere
OL,14,Fapologies.
OL,16,F"We also acknowledge that in our
OL,17,Fdecision making, we did not adequately
OL,18,Fconsider your concerns, formally or
OL,19,Finformally and we sincerely regret
OL,20,Fthat we were unable to get this right.
OL,1,W~k4~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}        G4/15
OL,2,W/*%+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNE Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,394,390,120,260,000,100
PN,39305
SC,0005
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F393A1782397117
OL,3,CDarlington nurses due #187,000 in
OL,4,Cdamages over single-sex changing rooms
OL,5,Crow
OL,7,F"In light of the judgment, we have
OL,8,Freviewed our policies and the changes
OL,9,Fthat have already been put in place
OL,10,Fand will consider what facilities are
OL,11,Frequired to follow the Tribunal's
OL,12,Ffindings in a way that is respectful
OL,13,Fto all of our colleagues."
OL,15,FThe letter continues: "The Trust is
OL,16,Fcommitted to ensuring that we support
OL,17,Fall colleagues and is committed to
OL,18,Fdoing so through our respective
OL,19,Fpolicies, procedures and actions as
OL,20,Fwell as learning from the findings of
OL,21,Fthis judgment.
OL,1,W~k4~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}        G5/15
OL,2,W/*%+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNE Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,394,390,120,260,000,100
PN,39306
SC,0006
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F393A1782397117
OL,3,CDarlington nurses due #187,000 in
OL,4,Cdamages over single-sex changing rooms
OL,5,Crow
OL,7,F"We know that this has been a
OL,8,Fdifficult and distressing experience
OL,9,Ffor you. We also recognise that, at
OL,10,Ftimes, your concerns were not fully
OL,11,Fheard or addressed in a timely or
OL,12,Fsensitive manner, and we regret the
OL,13,Fimpact this had on you and colleagues
OL,14,Fwho have been affected by this process
OL,15,Fand subsequent judgment."
OL,1,W~k4~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}        G6/15
OL,2,W/*%+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNE Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,394,390,120,260,000,100
PN,39307
SC,0007
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F393A1782397117
OL,3,CDarlington nurses due #187,000 in
OL,4,Cdamages over single-sex changing rooms
OL,5,Crow
OL,7,FResponding to the letter, Bethany
OL,8,FHutchison, President of the Darlington
OL,9,FNursing Union, said: "We have done
OL,10,Fthis, not just for ourselves, but for
OL,11,Four colleagues who were too afraid or
OL,12,Funable to speak up, and for every
OL,13,Fwoman and girl in the country.
OL,15,F"We raised our concerns because we
OL,16,Fbelieved something was seriously
OL,17,Fwrong, not just for us, but for the
OL,18,Fprotection of all women in the NHS.
OL,19,FInstead of being listened to, we were
OL,20,Fignored, labelled, and subjected to
OL,21,Fpressure and intimidation.
OL,1,W~k4~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}        G7/15
OL,2,W/*%+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNE Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,394,390,120,260,000,100
PN,39308
SC,0008
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F393A1782397117
OL,3,CDarlington nurses due #187,000 in
OL,4,Cdamages over single-sex changing rooms
OL,5,Crow
OL,7,F"This outcome is a vindication of our
OL,8,Fstand for dignity, privacy, and common
OL,9,Fsense. We hope it ensures that no
OL,10,Fwoman is ever again made to feel
OL,11,Funsafe in her workplace for speaking
OL,12,Fthe truth."
OL,14,FThe seven nurses who brought the case
OL,15,F- Bethany Hutchison, Lisa Lockey,
OL,16,FKaren Danson, Tracy Hooper, Annice
OL,17,FGrundy, Carly Hoy and Jane Peveller -
OL,18,Fwere supported by the Christian Legal
OL,19,FCentre in their claim.
OL,1,W~k4~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}        G8/15
OL,2,W/*%+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNE Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,394,390,120,260,000,100
PN,39309
SC,0009
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F393A1782397117
OL,3,CDarlington nurses due #187,000 in
OL,4,Cdamages over single-sex changing rooms
OL,5,Crow
OL,7,FChief Executive of the Christian Legal
OL,8,FCentre Andrea Williams said: "This
OL,9,Fcase sends a powerful message across
OL,10,Fthe NHS and beyond that ideology
OL,11,Fcannot override those fundamental
OL,12,Fduties."
OL,14,FThe nurses filed legal proceedings
OL,15,Fagainst the trust with the Newcastle
OL,16,FEmployment Tribunal in 2024, on the
OL,17,Fgrounds of sexual harassment and sex
OL,18,Fdiscrimination.
OL,1,W~k4~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}        G9/15
OL,2,W/*%+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNE Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,394,390,120,260,000,100
PN,39310
SC,0010
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F393A1782397117
OL,3,CDarlington nurses due #187,000 in
OL,4,Cdamages over single-sex changing rooms
OL,5,Crow
OL,7,FThe judgement of the tribunal in
OL,8,FJanuary 2026 rejected the nurses'
OL,9,Fclaims that the colleague in question,
OL,10,Fnamed Rose Henderson, had personally
OL,11,Fengaged in conduct that amounted to
OL,12,Fharassment.
OL,14,FDuring the tribunal hearings, Rose
OL,15,Ftold the panel: "I am not the
OL,16,Findividual (the claimants) have
OL,17,Fpainted me to be", and described how
OL,18,F"upsetting" it had been to see "hordes
OL,19,Fof people" posting insults online
OL,20,Fafter the case came to public
OL,21,Fattention.
OL,1,W~k4~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}       G10/15
OL,2,W/*%+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNE Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,394,390,120,260,000,100
PN,39311
SC,0011
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F393A1782397117
OL,3,CDarlington nurses due #187,000 in
OL,4,Cdamages over single-sex changing rooms
OL,5,Crow
OL,7,FThe tribunal judgement also rejected
OL,8,Fthe claim that the trust had
OL,9,Fvictimised the claimants.
OL,11,FSubscribe for free to our weekly
OL,12,Fnewsletter for exclusive and original
OL,13,Fcoverage from ITV News. Direct to your
OL,14,Finbox every Friday morning.
OL,1,W~k4~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}       G11/15
OL,2,W/*%+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNE Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,394,390,120,260,000,100
PN,39312
SC,0012
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F393A1782397117
OL,3,CDarlington nurses due #187,000 in
OL,4,Cdamages over single-sex changing rooms
OL,5,Crow
OL,7,FCounty Durham and Darlington NHS
OL,8,FFoundation Trust confirmed it had
OL,9,Freached an agreement with the nurses
OL,10,Fand has offered a formal apology
OL,11,F"acknowledging the tribunal's findings
OL,12,Fand the impact the matters considered
OL,13,Fby the tribunal had on those involved".
OL,26,@uD@fO]
OL,1,W~k4~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}       G12/15
OL,2,W/*%+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNE Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,394,390,120,260,000,100
PN,39313
SC,0013
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F393A1782397117
OL,3,CDarlington nurses due #187,000 in
OL,4,Cdamages over single-sex changing rooms
OL,5,Crow
OL,7,FIt said that, since the judgment was
OL,8,Fissued, the trust has undertaken
OL,9,Ffurther work, including ensuring that
OL,10,Funisex facilities are available across
OL,11,Fits hospital sites and "continuing to
OL,12,Freview relevant policies and
OL,13,Fprocedures to ensure they reflect the
OL,14,Ftribunal's findings and the trust's
OL,15,Fresponsibilities as a public body".
OL,17,FChief executive Steve Russell said:
OL,18,F"We have accepted and respected the
OL,19,Ftribunal's findings from the outset
OL,20,Fand have carefully considered what
OL,21,Fthey mean for our organisation.
OL,1,W~k4~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}       G13/15
OL,2,W/*%+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNE Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,394,390,120,260,000,100
PN,39314
SC,0014
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F393A1782397117
OL,3,CDarlington nurses due #187,000 in
OL,4,Cdamages over single-sex changing rooms
OL,5,Crow
OL,7,F"We recognise that the approach taken
OL,8,Fshould have been different, and we
OL,9,Fregret the impact this had on the
OL,10,Fcolleagues involved.
OL,12,F"We have repeated our apology directly
OL,13,Fto those affected."
OL,15,FMr Russell said: "Following the
OL,16,Fjudgment, we issued updated guidance
OL,17,Fand developed unisex facilities to
OL,18,Fensure that single sex facilities are
OL,19,Fused based on biological sex.
OL,1,W~k4~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}       G14/15
OL,2,W/*%+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNE Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,394,390,120,260,000,100
PN,39315
SC,0015
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F393A1782397117
OL,3,CDarlington nurses due #187,000 in
OL,4,Cdamages over single-sex changing rooms
OL,5,Crow
OL,7,F"Whilst this complies with the
OL,8,Fjudgment we want to further improve
OL,9,Fchanging facilities for all colleagues.
OL,11,F"We also have to acknowledge the
OL,12,Fimpact these changes have had on some
OL,13,Fof our other colleagues.
OL,15,F"Our focus now is on moving forward,
OL,16,Fcontinuing to support our colleagues
OL,17,Fand ensuring our policies, facilities
OL,18,Fand practices reflect both our legal
OL,19,Fresponsibilities and our commitment to
OL,20,Fproviding an inclusive workplace for
OL,21,Feveryone."
OL,1,W~k4~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}       G15/15
OL,2,W/*%+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,,,
